<H3> <TI>   Interior Minister Forced To Resign </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Interior Minister Forced To Resign </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR3105153494 Amsterdam HET FINANCIEELE DAGBLAD in Dutch 30 
May 94 p 1 </F>

<F P=103> BR3105153494 </F>
