<F P=100> GERMANY </F>
<H3> <TI>   Russia Seeks Compensation for Former Properties </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Russia Seeks Compensation for Former Properties </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2905104594 Berlin N-TV in German 1000 GMT 29 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2905104594 </F>
<F P=104>  Berlin N-TV </F>
<F P=105>  German </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Russia is lodging claims worth billions [currency 
unspecified] against Germany in respect of property in eastern 
Germany, according to FOCUS magazine. Moscow is demanding the 
restitution of at least 1,200 buildings and plots of land, 
including prime sites in the most expensive areas of Berlin, 
Dresden, and Leipzig. More than 100 sites were legally acquired 
in the 1950's by the Soviet Foreign Trade Office. 

</TEXT>

