<H3> <TI>   Justice Minister Responds </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Justice Minister Responds </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR3105154494 Rome LA REPUBBLICA in Italian 30 May 94 p 6 </F>
