<H3> <TI>   Defense Minister Urges Public To Fight Terrorism </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Defense Minister Urges Public To Fight Terrorism </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0106173494 Madrid Teletexto TVE in Spanish 1615 GMT 1 Jun 
94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0106173494 </F>
<F P=104>  Madrid Teletexto TVE </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


