<H3> <TI>   Helicopter Crash Deals Blow to Intelligence Work </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Helicopter Crash Deals Blow to Intelligence Work </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM0306100294 London THE GUARDIAN in English 3 Jun 94 p 
2--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> PM0306100294 </F>
<F P=104>  London THE GUARDIAN </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
