<H3> <TI>   Balance of Payments Shows 4 Trillion Surplus </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Balance of Payments Shows 4 Trillion Surplus </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR2505152494 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 1130 GMT 25 
May 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

